The following matrix A depends on a parameter p. Find all the values of
of the parameter p for which the corresponding matrix is not invertible.

\begin{align*}
A=\begin{bmatrix}
1  &  2  &  3  &  4\\
100  &  200  &  300  &  401\\
0  &  p  &  p+1  &  p+2\\
0  &  -p  &  -2p+1  &  -3p+2
\end{bmatrix}
\end{align*}
